      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "生捻须吟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "六经蕴藉胸中久，一剑十年磨在手⋯⋯",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那书生一笑接吟：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "便道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "心想这女孩儿原来十分聪明，倒不可不出个极难的题目来难难她，四下一望，见山边一排棕榈，树叶随风而动，宛若挥扇，他即景生情，摇了摇手中的摺扇，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "游目四顾，只见对面平地上有一座小小寺院，庙前有个荷塘，此时七月将尽，高山早寒，荷叶已然凋了大半，心中一动，笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那书生道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那书生道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉指着他头上戴的逍遥巾道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "猛然想起少年时在塾中读书之时，老师曾说过一个绝对，数十年来无人能对得工整，说不得，只好难她一难，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那书生不信，心道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "请罢。",
