      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉一转头，见那书生与农夫脸上显得又焦急又关切，心中大为疑惑：",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉道：",
