      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉道：",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一灯见她兴奋惊讶之下，颊现晕红，其实已吃力异常，只强运内力撑住，伸手扶住她右臂，说道：",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "扶着她慢慢走向旁边厢房，将到门口，那书生和农夫突然互使个眼色，抢在门口，同时跪下，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "一灯摇头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们功力够么？能医得好么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一灯大师脸色微沉，道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_deng_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "一灯大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那书生道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一灯大师叹了口气道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说着将画递给了他。那农夫磕头道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "医伤治病，怎地有恁大干系？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖答应了。一灯闭了双眼，忽又睁眼说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "心中更加诧异：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一灯一笑，道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "点穴章",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "南帝",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一阳指",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咳，天下竟有这等功夫！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "凝神观看一灯的趋退转折，抢攻固然神妙，尤难的却是在一攻而退，鱼逝兔脱，无比灵动，忽然心想：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "一人大",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "师父！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 536,
      "line_end": 536
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "神龙摆尾",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "那书生怒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "完啦，还阻拦什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 544
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖听她说话，喜悦无已，颤声道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 554,
      "line_end": 554
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉转头四望，摇了摇头，笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 556
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 562
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一灯喜道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 566,
      "line_end": 566
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那书生急道：",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 574,
      "line_end": 574
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一灯拗不过他，自感内力耗竭，从他手中将数十粒九花玉露丸都吞服了，喝了几口清水，对郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 576,
      "line_end": 576
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "回头对郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 586,
      "line_end": 586
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖忙问：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 592,
      "line_end": 592
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一灯微笑不语。黄蓉心道：",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 592,
      "line_end": 592
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 602,
      "line_end": 602
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一灯道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 604,
      "line_end": 604
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉大吃一惊，心道：",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 606,
      "line_end": 606
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "忙道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 608,
      "line_end": 608
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "众人听到",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 616,
      "line_end": 616
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两字，齐声惊呼。那书生道：",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 616,
      "line_end": 616
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一灯微笑道：",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 618,
      "line_end": 618
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一灯道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 628,
      "line_end": 628
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉当下说了黑沼茅屋中的情状，并道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 628,
      "line_end": 628
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那农夫厉声道：",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 630,
      "line_end": 630
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一灯只叹道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 636,
      "line_end": 636
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "脸色随即转为慈和，对靖蓉二人道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 636,
      "line_end": 636
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "说",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "请用饭。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 646,
      "line_end": 646
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一个老和尚尖声道：",
